      <description><![CDATA[<b>The Underground (And Surface) Exhibition</b><br><i>Arts &amp; Culture</i><br>Fri 27th Feb – Sun 20th Sep<br>Guildhall Yard, City of London<br>pay what you can<br><br>Jock McFadyen's large-scale Tube station paintings from the late 1990s with a soundscape by Jem Finer, transforming familiar stations to rethink how you see the Underground.<br><br><a href="https://www.designmynight.com/london/blog/things-to-do-in-london-this-weekend">More info / tickets</a>]]></description>
